《怪兽大学》的第一段[[预告片|预告片]]于2012年6月20日发布<ref name="ColliderTeaserTrailer">{{cite news | author=Matt Goldberg| url=http://collider.com/monsters-university-trailers-images/174081/ | title=Four Teaser Trailers and Six Images for Pixar’s MONSTERS UNIVERSITY [Updated] | date=2012-06-20 | accessdate=2013-11-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029211519/http://collider.com/monsters-university-trailers-images/174081/ |archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref>。这部预告片一共有四个版本，其中麦克在睡梦中嘟囔着各种借口拒绝上学，如“我不能上学，（因为）我没穿衣服”、“我的家庭作业把我的狗吃掉了”、“班长？”和“我的小马驹上了校长的名单。”第二段预告片于2013年2月11日发布，第三部在2013年4月26日，第四部，也是最后的一部，于2013年5月30日发布，其中包含有电影中的镜头。<ref>{{cite web |title='Monsters University' Trailer: See Mike And Sully Before They Were Scary (VIDEO) |date=2012-06-20 |author=Kia Makarechi |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-11-11 |deadurl=no |url= http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/06/20/monsters-university-trailer-teaser-video_n_1610673.html |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131111085424/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/06/20/monsters-university-trailer-teaser-video_n_1610673.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://trailers.apple.com/trailers/disney/monstersuniversity/ |title=Monsters University - Movie Trailers |work=iTunes |publisher=Apple Inc. |accessdate=2013-11-15 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-11-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106040314/http://trailers.apple.com/trailers/disney/monstersuniversity/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |accessdate=2013-07-12 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2013-07-12 |title=Monsters University- Trailers |work=Yahoo Movies! |publisher=Yahoo! Inc. |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130712213811/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/monsters-university/trailers/monsters-university-teaser-trailer-29717274.html |url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/monsters-university/trailers/monsters-university-teaser-trailer-29717274.html}}</ref>

