== 反响 ==

=== 专业评价 ===
《怪兽大学》所获评价以正面为主。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的175篇评论文章，其中137篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为78%，平均得分6.8（最高10分）。该网站上的共识评价中称，影片虽然“没有达到皮克斯最出色作品的高度，但对于任何年龄段观众来说《怪兽大学》仍然是一部风趣而体贴的家庭娱乐作品”<ref>{{cite web |title=Monsters University (2013) |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/monsters_university/ |publisher= Flixster |work= Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate=2013-11-14 |archivedate=2013-10-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131030062512/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/monsters_university/}}</ref>。而从[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的41篇评论来看，其中26篇给出好评，无差评，15篇褒贬不一，平均得分65（满分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/monsters-university |title=Monsters University|publisher= CBS Interactive | work = Metacritic |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archivedate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130921055037/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/monsters-university}}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的马特·佐勒·塞茨（{{lang|en|Matt Zoller Seitz}}）给予影片四星的高度评价（最高四星），称其中体现了《怪兽电力公司》的“真正精神，符合其基调。但在情节上并没有呈现出彻底的创新”<ref>{{cite web |last=Zoller |first=Matt |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/monsters-university-2013 |title=Monsters University Movie Review (2013) |publisher=Roger Ebert |date=2013-07-10 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195326/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/monsters-university-2013}}</ref>。“{{lang|en|[[Time_Out|Time Out]]}}”[[杂志|杂志]]的特雷弗·约翰斯顿（{{lang|en|Trevor Johnston}}）给予本片四星评价（最高五星），认为对于一部纯粹的前传来说，《怪兽大学》的表现是到位的，其中也有足够多的内容可以唤起观众对《怪兽电力公司》那毛茸茸的可爱回忆<ref>{{cite web |author=Trevor Johnston |url=http://www.timeout.com/london/film/monsters-university |title=Monsters University | review, synopsis, book tickets, showtimes, movie release date | Time Out London |publisher=Timeout.com |date=2013-07-12 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029191424/http://www.timeout.com/london/film/monsters-university}}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的克里斯·纳什瓦提（{{lang|en|Chris Nashawaty}}）给出{{lang|en|A−}}的评价（最高{{lang|en|A+}}），称影片让人恢复了对皮克斯的信心，因为之前的《赛车总动员2》让人担心皮克斯是不是已经失去了想像力。看到麦克和萨利见面时那些令人愉快的故事后，这些担心也都随之烟消云散了<ref>{{cite news|author=Chris Nashawaty |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20483133_20687785,00.html |title=Monsters University Movie Review | Movie Reviews and News | Summer Movies – Calendar, Trailers, Movie Photos, Movie Clips, Movie Guide |deadurl=no |publisher=EW.com |date=2013-05-30 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013220017/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20483133_20687785%2C00.html }}</ref>。《[[费城问询报|费城问询报]]》的史蒂芬·里耶（{{lang|en|Steven Rea}}）对本片的评价为三星（最高四星），称赞电影既可爱又搞笑，其动画表现虽然还没有到给人启迪的程度，但无疑是丰富多彩的<ref>{{cite web |author=Steven Rea, Inquirer Movie Columnist and Critic |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029184402/http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/20130621__Monsters_University__gives_it_the_old_college_try.html |url=http://www.philly.com/philly/entertainment/movies/20130621__Monsters_University__gives_it_the_old_college_try.html |title='Monsters University' gives it the old college try |publisher=Philly.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-15}}</ref>。[[美联社|美联社]]的杰克·科伊尔（{{lang|en|Jake Coyle}}）给本片三星评级（最高四星），称其表现虽说没有像皮克斯其他作品那么有天赋，但仍然是一部好电影<ref>{{cite web |last=Coyle |first=Jake |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195954/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/review-monsters-university-gets-passing-grade |url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/review-monsters-university-gets-passing-grade |title=Review: 'Monsters University' gets a passing grade |publisher=Bigstory.ap.org |date= |accessdate=2013-11-15}}</ref>。

《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》杂志的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]给影片的评价为三星，称其虽然有些缺乏原创性，但趣味性还是很有感染力。克里斯托和古德曼无疑是这种让人骨子里发痒喜剧艺术的大师<ref>{{cite web |author= Peter Travers |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/monsters-university-20130620 |title=Peter Travers Reviews 'Monsters University' | Movie Reviews |publisher=Rolling Stone |date= |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130701095651/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/monsters-university-20130620 |archivedate=2013-07-01 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》周刊的理查德·科利斯（{{lang|en|Richard Corliss}}）也给予本片正面评价，称赞这部非常有魅力的小电影仍然值得让孩子们拖着家长走进电影院，再看一眼衣柜里的怪物和皮克斯那些熟悉的内容<ref>{{cite news |last=Corliss |first=Richard |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=no |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2013/06/13/pixars-monsters-university-when-hairy-met-scary/ |title=Movie Review: Pixar's 'Monsters University' - When Hairy Met Scary | TIME.com |publisher=Entertainment.time.com |date=2013-06-13 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029234933/http://entertainment.time.com/2013/06/13/pixars-monsters-university-when-hairy-met-scary/}}</ref>。

《{{link-en|亚利桑那共和报|The Arizona Republic}}》的比尔·古迪科恩兹（{{lang|en|Bill Goodykoontz}}）对本片的评价为三星半（最高五星），称“像这样的电影根本就没有任何理由要存在，可一旦你看过之后，你又会为其存在感到高兴”<ref>{{cite web |title=‘Monsters University,’ 3.5 stars |author=Bill Goodykoontz |date=2013-06-20 |url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/movies/articles/20130617monsters-university-movie-review-goodykoontz.html?nclick_check=1 |publisher=The Arizona Republic}}</ref>。《{{link-en|乡村之声|The Village Voice}}》的阿兰·谢尔斯图尔（{{lang|en|Alan Scherstuhl}}）也给出正面评价，称《怪兽大学》感觉起来不像是那种急于表达出什么的艺-{}-术家的作品，而是以孩子们的喜好程度为基础。技术上影片给人留下了深刻的印象，不过没有达到一个更有意义的高度<ref>{{cite web |author=Alan Scherstuhl |archivedate=2013-10-29 |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2013-06-19/film/pixar-bangs-out-more-superior-kids-fare-with-monsters-university-and-nothing-more/ |title=Pixar Bangs Out More Superior Kids Fare with Monsters University, And Nothing More - Page 1 - Movies - New York |publisher=Village Voice |date=2013-06-19 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029183928/http://www.villagevoice.com/2013-06-19/film/pixar-bangs-out-more-superior-kids-fare-with-monsters-university-and-nothing-more/ }}</ref>。

《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》的克劳迪娅·普格（{{lang|en|Claudia Puig}}）对电影的评级为三星（最高四星），称其“或者不像《怪兽电力公司》那么有创造性，但仍然是皮克斯风趣幽默而又和蔼可亲的动画作品”<ref>{{cite news |author= Claudia Puig |url= http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/06/20/monsters-university-review/2367049/ |title= It won't make honor roll, but 'Monsters University' easily passes |work= USA Today |date=  |accessdate= 2013-11-15 |quote= may not be as inventive as ''Inc.'', but it's an amusing and amiable addition to Pixar's roster of animated coming-of-age stories. |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130928021019/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/06/20/monsters-university-review/2367049/ |archive-date= 2013-09-28 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的迈克尔·O·萨利文（{{lang|en|Michael O'Sullivan}}）也给出三星的评价（最高四星），称“电影中的虚构世界或许是由儿童的恐惧来供电，但《怪兽大学》还是由其中明星般的能量所点亮的”<ref>{{cite news |author=Michael O’Sullivan |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/monsters-university-movie-review/2013/06/20/3acd44ec-d459-11e2-b05f-3ea3f0e7bb5a_story.html |title=‘Monsters University’ movie review |publisher=The Washington Post |date=2013-05-23 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |quote=It may be children’s terror that powers the movie’s fictional universe, but it’s the energy of its stars that lights up ''Monsters University''. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110075307/http://www.washingtonpost.com/goingoutguide/movies/monsters-university-movie-review/2013/06/20/3acd44ec-d459-11e2-b05f-3ea3f0e7bb5a_story.html |archive-date=2014-01-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{lang|en|ReelViews}}网站在线影评人詹姆斯·伯拉迪尼（{{lang|en|James Berardinelli}}）对本片的评价也是三星（最高四星），他写道：“虽然与皮克斯与迪士尼长斯合作期间推出的其他作品相比还是有所不足，但仍然值得为它而走进电影院，特别是对孩子们来说。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reelviews.net/php_review_template.php?identifier=2633&utm_source=feedly |title=Reelviews Movie Reviews |publisher=Reelviews.net |date=2013-06-21 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |quote=Although it falls short of the best Pixar has brought to the screen over its long association with Disney, it's nevertheless worth a trip to the theater, especially for kids. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031065429/http://www.reelviews.net/php_review_template.php?identifier=2633&utm_source=feedly |archive-date=2013-10-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

不过也有些影评人对电影反响不佳。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》的泰·布尔（{{lang|en|Ty Burr}}）给电影两颗半星评价（最高四星），表示“这电影不算差，对少部分儿童还说可能还很不错。但对于一个曾拍出《[[飞屋环游记|飞屋环游记]]》、《[[瓦力_(电影)|瓦力]]》、《[[超人总动员|超人总动员]]》和《玩具总动员》系列的公司来说，这样的作品也就是个接近一般的水平”<ref>{{cite news |last=Burr |first=Ty |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029214616/http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/2013/06/19/movie-review-pixar-gives-the-old-college-try-monsters-university/xYO6QmNfHT4V98wvOBCh7L/story.html |url=http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/2013/06/19/movie-review-pixar-gives-the-old-college-try-monsters-university/xYO6QmNfHT4V98wvOBCh7L/story.html |title=Movie review: Pixar gives it the old college try in ‘Monsters University’ – Movies |publisher=Boston.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-15 |quote=This is not a bad movie, and to small children it will be a very good one, but it’s closer to average than one would wish from the company that gave us ''Up'', ''WALL-E'', ''The Incredibles'', and the ''Toy Story'' series.}}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的玛诺拉·达吉斯（{{lang|en|Manohla Dargis}}）给出两星半的评价（最高五星），她在评价中批评前传不但失去了《怪兽电力公司》的原创性，连那种复杂的情感波动，那种与人类世界相似的精致的痛苦和感动，全都无影无踪了<ref>{{cite news |quote=Both the originality and stirring emotional complexity of ''Monsters, Inc.'', with its exquisitely painful and touching parallels with the human world, are missing. |archivedate=2013-06-21 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/21/movies/monsters-university-unfolds-before-monsters-inc.html?_r=1& | title=A College Where the Exams Are Terrifying | publisher=The New York Times Company | work=The New York Times | date=2013-06-20 | accessdate=2013-11-15 | author=Dargis, Manohla |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130621104849/http://movies.nytimes.com/2013/06/21/movies/monsters-university-unfolds-before-monsters-inc.html}}</ref>。

《{{link-en|明星纪事报|The Star-Ledger|纽瓦克明星纪事报}}》的斯蒂芬·威蒂（{{lang|en|Stephen Whitty}}）给本片的评价也是两星半（最高四星），称这是一部巧夺天工的完整艺术品。G级的评级非常精准，因为片中没有任何插科打诨，也没有任何通过暗指流行文化内容来向成年人抛出的让人厌倦的旁枝末节<ref>{{cite web|author=  Stephen Whitty | work = The Star-Ledger | date = 2013-06-20 |quote=The artwork is accomplished, and intricate. The G-rating is genuine, without any gross-out gags. And there's none of the usual winks to the adults with tired, pop-culture references. |url= http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2013/06/monsters_university_review_pixar_gets_a_passing_grade.html |title= 'Monsters University' review: Pixar gets a passing grade |publisher= NJ.com |accessdate= 2013-11-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195611/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2013/06/monsters_university_review_pixar_gets_a_passing_grade.html |archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref>。{{link-en|理查德·罗伊伯|Richard Roeper}}给本片两星半的评价（最高五星），称对于一个很少会冒风险的制片公司来说，本片四半八稳，毫无惊喜，甚至有些平淡无奇<ref>{{cite web |quote=This is a safe, predictable, edge-free, nearly bland effort from a studio that rarely hedges its bets. |url=http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/monstersuniversity.aspx |title=Monsters University Review |publisher=RichardRoeper.com |date= |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029194736/http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/monstersuniversity.aspx |deadurl=no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]}}网站的{{link-en|伦纳德·马尔丁|Leonard Maltin}}称赞了电影的动画制作和艺术指导，但也表示自己希望其剧情不会如此沉重并且更加有趣，他还在文章中写道，皮克斯把动画长片提升到了一个如此的高度，以致于当他们推出的一部电影只能算良好，还没有到达了不起的程度时，评论家就会大肆批评，对于这一点，皮克斯实在是自做自受<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/leonardmaltin/monsters-university |title=Monsters University - Leonard Maltin - Blogs - Indiewire |publisher=IndieWire |work=Leonard Maltin |accessdate=2013-11-15 |quote=Pixar has raised the bar for animated features so high that when they turn out a film that’s merely good, instead of great, they have only themselves to blame for causing critics to damn them with faint praise. |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029190530/http://blogs.indiewire.com/leonardmaltin/monsters-university }}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》的迈克尔·菲利普斯（{{lang|en|Michael Phillips}}）给电影两星评价（最高四星），称《怪兽大学》是《怪兽电力公司》一部毫无魅力到让人感觉奇怪的前传，表现平淡无奇，与其他动画制片公司用来打发时间的续集相比也毫无过人之处<ref>{{cite news |author=Michael Phillips |date=2013-06-20 |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/sc-mov-0618-monsters-university-20130620,0,6683505.column |title=Monsters University movie review by Chicago Tribune's Michael Phillips |publisher=chicagotribune.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029183902/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/sc-mov-0618-monsters-university-20130620%2C0%2C6683505.column |accessdate=2013-11-16 }}</ref>。《{{link-en|迈阿密先驱报|The Miami Herald}}》的勒内·罗德里格斯（{{lang|en|Rene Rodriguez}}）给本片的评价为两星（最高五星），批评电影制作人员没有尽到自己最大的努力，甚至半心半意到让人感觉有些懒散<ref>{{cite web|last=Rodriguez |first=Rene |archivedate=2013-09-21 |url=http://www.miami.com/039monsters-university039-g-article |title='Monsters University' (G) |publisher=miami.com |date=2013-06-20 |accessdate=2013-11-16 |quote=feels half-hearted and lazy, like they weren't even trying. At least show a little effort, guys. |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054453/http://www.miami.com/039monsters-university039-g-article}}</ref>。

《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》的托德·麦卡锡（{{lang|en|Todd McCarthy}}）对电影的评价为负面，称其中“毫无惊喜”，要么是在让人意想不到的地方开始沉沦，要么就是堆彻着皮克斯最棒故事中的那些内容。无论哪一种，都远远没有达到应有的想像力水准<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/monsters-university/review/564746 |deadurl=no |title=Monsters University Review |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |date=2013-06-09 |accessdate=2013-11-16 |first=Todd |last=McCarthy |archivedate=2013-11-12 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131112063553/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/monsters-university/review/564746}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
截止2013年11月10日，《怪兽大学》在北美进账为2亿6818万6282美元，其他国家4亿7506万6843美元，全球总票房7亿4325万3125美元，如果不计[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]因素，其成绩可以在历史上所有的电影中[[最高电影票房收入列表|名列第53位]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/ |title=All Time Worldwide Box Office Grosses |work= Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archivedate=2013-11-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131108163600/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/}}</ref>，也可以在[[2013年电影|2013年电影]]中排到第4位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2013&p=.htm |title=2013 Yearly Box Office Results |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archivedate=2013-11-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111185411/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2013&p=.htm}}</ref>，是皮克斯所有作品中的全球票房[[季军|季军]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=pixar.htm |title=Pixar Movies at the Box Office |work= Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131023212703/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=pixar.htm |archivedate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，在历史上的所有动画片中则可以排到第9位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm |title=Animation Movies at the Box Office |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160819221907/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm |archive-date=2016-08-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片在世界各国上映首周的总票房为1亿3690万美元<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2013-10-14 |deadurl=no |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm |title= All Time Worldwide Opening Records |work= Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131014064534/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/worldwideopenings.htm}}</ref>。迪士尼拒绝透露电影的制作成本，《娱乐周刊》预计其数额将高于《[[勇敢传说|勇敢传说]]》的1.85亿美元，这主要是因为请约翰·古德曼和比利·克里斯托回归给其角色配音所需付出的高额片酬<ref name="EW1stWeekend">{{cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/06/23/box-office-report-monsters-university-world-war-z/ |title=Box office report: 'Monsters University' scares up $82 million, 'World War Z' shatters expectations |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |date= |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archivedate=2013-10-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131019213021/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/06/23/box-office-report-monsters-university-world-war-z/}}</ref>。{{lang|en|CraveOnline}}的子网站{{lang|en|Shockya}}预计本片的预算与《[[玩具总动员2|玩具总动员2]]》和《[[赛车总动员2|赛车总动员2]]》相等，约为2亿美元<ref name="Shockya" />。

==== 北美 ====
迪士尼公司预测《怪兽大学》上映首周将收入至少7000万美元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-monsters-university-571848 |title=Box Office Preview: 'Monsters University' Pacing to Beat 'World War Z' |author=Pamela McClintock |date=2013-06-19 |accessdate=2013-11-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111025729/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-preview-monsters-university-571848 |archivedate=2013-11-11 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |deadurl=no}}</ref>。影片于2013年6月21日（[[星期五|星期五]]）上映，当天就登上票房榜[[冠军|冠军]]宝座，收入3047万美元，其中包括[[星期四|星期四]]晚上20点夜场放映收入的260万美元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-brad-pitts-572656 |title=Box Office Report: Brad Pitt's 'World War Z' Opens to $3.6 Million Thursday Night |author=Pamela McClintock, Rebecca Ford |date=2013-06-21 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-11-11 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111025733/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-report-brad-pitts-572656}}</ref>，成为历史上上映首日票房排名第5位的动画电影<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2013-10-20 |deadurl=no |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/06/22/box-office-update-monsters-university-world-war-z/ |title=Box office update: 'Monsters University' and 'World War Z' have scary good Friday; 'Man of Steel' sinks|author=Grady Smith |date=2013-06-22 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131020064522/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/06/22/box-office-update-monsters-university-world-war-z/}}</ref>。影片上映首周收入8243万美元，截止2013年11月15日，这个成绩可以在皮克斯所有作品中名列第2位，仅次于[[2010年电影|2010年]]的《玩具总动员3》<ref name="wknd-rprt">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3695&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: 'Monsters' and Zombies Both Win On Busy Weekend |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=2013-06-23 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014015608/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3695&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-10-14 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，而在所有[[美国电影分级制度|G级评级]]电影中也可以排在第二位，同样排在《玩具总动员3》之后<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/mpaa.htm?page=G&p=.htm |title=Biggest Opening G Rated Movies |work= Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb |accessdate= 2013-11-15 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131014015339/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/mpaa.htm?page=G&p=.htm |archivedate=2013-10-14 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，在所有的前传电影中则名列第4位<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2013-10-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131020065324/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=prequel.htm&sort=opengross&order=DESC&p=.htm |url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=prequel.htm&sort=opengross&order=DESC&p=.htm |title=Prequel Movies |work= Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb |accessdate= 2013-11-15}}</ref>，在所有动画电影中排在第5位<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm&sort=opengross&order=DESC&p=.htm |title=Animation Movies (sorted by Opening) |work= Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb |accessdate= 2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020065229/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm&sort=opengross&order=DESC&p=.htm |deadurl=no}}</ref>，则在所有于6月发行的电影中也可以排名第5<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/month/?mo=06&p=.htm |title=Top June Opening Weekends |work= Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb |accessdate= 2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131020232255/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/month/?mo=06&p=.htm}}</ref>。《怪兽电力公司》第二周的票房与首周相比下降了45%，为4560万美元，但仍然排在票房榜首位<ref name="2ndwknd-rprt">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3697&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: 'Monsters' Repeats, 'Heat' Sets Fire to 'White House' |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=2013-06-30 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014023417/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3697&p=.htm |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-10-14}}</ref>。到了第三个星期，由于有来自《[[神偷奶爸2|神偷奶爸2]]》的强烈竞争，本片票房下滑了57%，收入1970万美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3700&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: 'Despicable' Defeats 'Ranger' Over Busy Fourth of July |publisher=Box Office Mojo |date=2013-07-07 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131014040417/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3700&p=.htm |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-10-14}}</ref>。截止2013年11月10日，《怪兽大学》是历史上票房第9高的动画电影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm |title=Animation Movies |work=Box Office Mojo |publisher=IMDb |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100823022307/http://boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=animation.htm |archive-date=2010-08-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====國際 ====
《怪兽电力公司》在35个国家和地区上映首周共收入5450万美元<ref name="wknd-rprt" />，并以3170万美元的成绩创下了迪士尼和皮克斯电影和[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]上映首周的票房新纪录<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/monsters-university-marks-disney-pixars-574206 |title='Monsters University' Marks Disney/Pixar's Top Latin America Opening |author=Agustin Mango |date=2013-06-24 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111025721/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/monsters-university-marks-disney-pixars-574206 |archivedate=2013-11-11 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |deadurl=no}}</ref>。电影在[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]以549万美元创下该国历史上首周电影票房的新纪录<ref>{{cite news |title=Disney•Pixar's 'Monsters University' Breaks Records in Latin America |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131019195816/https://thewaltdisneycompany.com/blog/disneypixar-monsters-university-breaks-records-latin-america |url=https://thewaltdisneycompany.com/blog/disneypixar-monsters-university-breaks-records-latin-america |first=David |last=Gill |date=2013-07-15 |publisher=Disney Post |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-19 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/argentina/?yr=2013&wk=25&p=new |title=Argentina Box Office June 20–23, 2013 |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020070143/http://boxofficemojo.com/intl/argentina/?yr=2013&wk=25&p=new |deadurl=no}}</ref>。《怪兽大学》在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]与《神偷奶爸2》同步上映，上映首周收入比后者少了356万美元，两部动画长片均不敌《[[僵尸世界大战|僵尸世界大战]]》，《怪兽大学》名列第3位<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Amazon |work=Box Office Mojo |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/australia/?yr=2013&wk=25&p=.htm |title=Australia Box Office June 20–23, 2013 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131020065559/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/australia/?yr=2013&wk=25&p=.htm}}</ref>。影片在[[香港|香港]]上映第一天收入503万[[港币|港币]]<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2013-10-19 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.filmbiz.asia/news/monsters-sets-hong-kong-animation-record |title=Monsters sets Hong Kong animation record |work=亚洲电影资讯 |author=Ma, Kevin |date=2013-07-12 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019205602/http://www.filmbiz.asia/news/monsters-sets-hong-kong-animation-record }}</ref>，首周收入2579万港币，单日最高793万港币，全面超越《玩具总动员3》，创下动画长片上映首日、首周和单日的票房新纪录<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/monsters-university-breaks-hong-kong-585462 |title='Monsters University' Breaks Another Hong Kong Box Office Record |first=Karen |last=Chu |date=2013-07-15 |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-11-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131111025724/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/monsters-university-breaks-hong-kong-585462}}</ref>，最終票房為7,740萬港幣<ref name="香港電影業資料彙編"/>。影片在台灣首日票房為新台幣2500萬元<ref name="首週">{{cite news |author1=許世穎 |title=票房車拚／《怪獸大學》破紀錄登頂 《末日》殺破1.6億 |url=https://www.nownews.com/news/20130701/210214 |work=[[NOWnews|NOWnews]] |date=2013-07-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180210180120/https://www.nownews.com/news/20130701/210214 |archivedate=2018-02-10}}</ref>；次週票房累計至新台幣1.5億元<ref>{{cite news |author1=許世穎 |title=票房車拚／《怪獸大學》再奪冠 《神偷奶爸》稱霸新片 |url=https://www.nownews.com/news/20130709/210218 |work=[[NOWnews|NOWnews]] |date=2013-07-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180210180140/https://www.nownews.com/news/20130709/210218 |archivedate=2018-02-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=《怪獸大學》不怕午後雷雨 蟬聯票房冠軍 |url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20130708003559-260404 |work=中時電子報 |date=2013-07-08 |access-date=2019-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190201065311/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20130708003559-260404 |archive-date=2019-02-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終全台票房為新台幣2.47億元<ref>{{cite news |author1=李世珍 |title=《鋼鐵人3》甩《玩命》《大尾》捲6億 登2013台灣票房王 |url=http://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20131223/35526341 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2013-12-13 |access-date=2018-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180225204958/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20131223/35526341 |archive-date=2018-02-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。电影在[[英国|英国]]上映首周以346万[[英镑|英镑]]登上票房榜冠军宝座<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a499068/monsters-university-beats-despicable-me-2-at-uk-box-office.html |title='Monsters University' beats 'Despicable Me 2' at UK box office – Movies News |publisher=Digital Spy |date=2013-06-27 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archivedate=2013-10-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131025193344/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a499068/monsters-university-beats-despicable-me-2-at-uk-box-office.html}}</ref>。不过电影在北美以外市场最成功的开场发生在[[中华人民共和国|中国大陆]]，共计收入1300万美元，在该国上映过的所有迪士尼电影首周票房中名列第4位<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.boxoffice.com/latest-news/2013-08-25-global-the-minions-take-over-the-world-with-8058m-total |title=GLOBAL: The Minions Take Over The World With $805.8M Total |publisher=boxoffice.com |date=2013-08-25 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105140845/http://www.boxoffice.com/latest-news/2013-08-25-global-the-minions-take-over-the-world-with-8058m-total |archivedate=2013-11-05 }}</ref><ref name="ovrs-mrkts">{{cite web |archivedate= 2013-10-20 |url= http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=monstersinc2.htm |title= Monsters University (2013) - International Box Office Results |work= Box Office Mojo |publisher= IMDb |accessdate= 2013-11-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131020065927/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=monstersinc2.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。《怪兽大学》在北美以外国家上映收入最高的是达到9010万美元的[[日本|日本]]，其次是收入4630万美元的英国、[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]和[[马尔他|马尔他]]，[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]以3760万美元排在第三位<ref name="ovrs-mrkts" />。

